<div >
    <div class="sfContentBlock sf-Long-text" ><div class="row about-our-company"><div class="col"><div class="card-group card-group-scroll"><div class="card shadow-sm"><img src="/images/default-source/homepage/about-our-company-tjx-success-factors.jpg?sfvrsn=1dcb267a_3" alt="" class="card-img-top"><div class="card-body d-flex flex-column"><h4 class="card-title">Success Factors</h4><p class="card-text">Over the course of our history, our strong financial results and cash generation have allowed us to simultaneously invest in the growth of the business and return cash to shareholders.
                    </p><a href="/investors/investor-information/success-factors" class="mt-auto card-link">Learn More</a>
 </div></div><div class="card shadow-sm"><img src="/images/default-source/homepage/card-about-our-company-tjx-how-we-do-it.jpg?sfvrsn=806dcbfe_3" class="card-img-top" alt=""><div class="card-body d-flex flex-column"><h4 class="card-title">How We Do It</h4><p class="card-text">TJX delivers great value on ever-changing selections of high quality, fashionable, brand name and designer merchandise at prices generally 20%-60% below full-price retailers (including department, specialty, and major online retailers) regular prices, on comparable merchandise, every day.</p><a href="/company/how-we-do-it" class="mt-auto card-link">Learn More</a>
 </div></div><div class="card shadow-sm"><img src="/images/default-source/homepage/about-our-company-tjx-inclusion-and-diversity.jpg?sfvrsn=82792534_2" class="card-img-top" alt=""><div class="card-body d-flex flex-column"><h4 class="card-title">Inclusion &amp; Diversity</h4><p class="card-text">We are strongly committed to continuing to build a more inclusive and diverse workplace where our Associates feel welcome in the Company, valued for their perspectives and contributions, and engaged with our business mission.
                    </p><a href="/corporate-responsibility/workplace/inclusion-diversity" class="mt-auto card-link">Learn More</a>
 </div></div><div class="card shadow-sm"><img src="/images/default-source/homepage/card-about-our-company-tjx-history.jpg?sfvrsn=9df7a7f0_2" class="card-img-top" alt=""><div class="card-body d-flex flex-column"><h4 class="card-title">TJX History</h4><p class="card-text">Our Company roots date back 45 years. In 1976, Bernard (Ben) Cammarata, General Merchandising Manager of Marshalls at the time, was recruited by discount retailer, Zayre Corp., to develop and spearhead the launch of a new off-price chain selling family apparel and home fashions. Under Mr. Cammaratas leadership, T.J. Maxx was born.
                    </p><a href="/company/history" class="mt-auto card-link">Learn More</a>
 </div></div></div></div></div></div>    
